maybe that's what it seems
like when you watch it,

00:20:52.042 --> 00:20:53.919
like he's running up with the wheelbarrow

00:20:53.919 --> 00:20:55.837
and he's just starting.
- I think it was,

00:20:55.837 --> 00:20:58.674
I think it started about her.

00:20:58.674 --> 00:20:59.549
- Hmm.
- And then-

00:20:59.549 --> 00:21:00.384
