00:21:35.794 --> 00:21:38.255
- I think that the
creative part of my brain

00:21:39.339 --> 00:21:43.051
and the political part of my
brain are intrinsically linked.

00:21:43.051 --> 00:21:46.263
Like I keep finding, like
every time I come up with

00:21:46.263 --> 00:21:51.268
like a movie or like, it's
more often than not political.

00:21:52.436 --> 00:21:56.148
I think it's 'cause that's how
I'm like digesting the world.

