00:22:05.699 --> 00:22:07.409
and it kind of feels-
- Yeah.

00:22:07.409 --> 00:22:09.661
- Very topical.
- Totally.

00:22:09.661 --> 00:22:12.331
- And you know, as we know
it, "Don't Look Up" together,

00:22:12.331 --> 00:22:14.416
it's very difficult to say something about

00:22:14.416 --> 00:22:15.792
the world we live in,

00:22:15.792 --> 00:22:19.254
and it has to have an element
of irony or comedy to it,

00:22:19.254 --> 00:22:21.673
otherwise people, they're not allowed in.

00:22:21.673 --> 00:22:23.759
You know what I mean, it feels like, oh,

00:22:23.759 --> 00:22:25.594
I'm watching these people's vocation

00:22:25.594 --> 00:22:28.263
and they, you know, do I relate to them?

00:22:28.263 --> 00:22:30.557
And the messiness of the comedy I think is

00:22:31.850 --> 00:22:34.436
