00:22:46.281 --> 00:22:47.657
you're alienating-

00:22:47.657 --> 00:22:49.076
- Half.
- You know, yeah.

00:22:49.076 --> 00:22:50.911
It's true, right?
- Yeah.

00:22:50.911 --> 00:22:54.122
- So this, I think Paul delicate balance

00:22:54.122 --> 00:22:57.626
and I think he did an
amazing job with this movie

00:22:57.626 --> 00:22:59.920
and saying something.
- I agree.

00:23:00.879 --> 00:23:02.506
I agree.

00:23:02.506 --> 00:23:04.508
It reminded me of not the movie,

00:23:04.508 --> 00:23:07.469
