00:23:11.223 --> 00:23:13.683
- What are your good and
bad habits as an actor?

00:23:15.644 --> 00:23:17.479
And can I answer for you?
No, I'm just kidding.

00:23:17.479 --> 00:23:20.524
- Yes, by the way, that'd be much better.

00:23:21.358 --> 00:23:23.235
Bad habits.

00:23:23.235 --> 00:23:25.821
I think I shoot out a lot of-

00:23:25.821 --> 00:23:27.656
- You shoot up?
- Ideas

00:23:27.656 --> 00:23:29.533
sometimes unnecessarily.

00:23:30.742 --> 00:23:33.412
Well it's kind of like a shotgun spray

00:23:33.412 --> 00:23:35.956
of anything that comes to mind,

00:23:35.956 --> 00:23:38.708
and a lot of that may waste time

00:23:38.708 --> 00:23:41.294
for the focus of what we already know,

00:23:41.294 --> 00:23:42.421
do you know what I'm saying?

00:23:42.421 --> 00:23:44.256
- Yeah, but that sounds helpful.

00:23:44.256 --> 00:23:46.633
'Cause if it's not useful
then you just move on.

00:23:46.633 --> 00:23:48.677
But if it is useful, that's
like really important.

00:23:48.677 --> 00:23:53.682
- Well sometimes maybe it steers
away from what is obvious,

00:23:53.723 --> 00:23:55.267
do you know what I mean?

00:23:55.267 --> 00:23:56.393
But yeah-
- that still sounds like

00:23:56.393 --> 00:23:57.727
a good thing to me.

00:23:57.727 --> 00:23:59.604
- Does it? I don't know.
- Steering away

00:23:59.604 --> 00:24:01.314
from what is obvious.
- Well, well you know,

00:24:01.314 --> 00:24:03.150
but sometimes it's unnecessary,

00:24:03.150 --> 00:24:05.444
like, you know, we know what
the scene's about let's,

00:24:05.444 --> 00:24:08.697
and I just keep coming
up with this stuff that

00:24:08.697 --> 00:24:10.449
may seem unnecessary, that's all.

00:24:10.449 --> 00:24:11.825
- Well, a broken clock is

00:24:11.825 --> 00:24:13.160
right twice a day.
- There you go.

00:24:13.160 --> 00:24:16.455
So I think there are
inevitably gonna be moments

00:24:16.455 --> 00:24:17.539
where it's not necessary,

00:24:17.539 --> 00:24:20.459
but I don't think that that
means the whole process is bad.

00:24:20.459 --> 00:24:22.043
- So maybe it's a-
- I think it's a good habit.

00:24:22.043 --> 00:24:23.170
- Maybe it's a good and bad thing,

00:24:23.170 --> 00:24:26.006
I answered both in one.
- Great.

00:24:26.006 --> 00:24:28.508
- Now I'm gonna throw that back on you.

00:24:28.508 --> 00:24:33.472
- My bad habit is that I am so good at

00:24:33.472 --> 00:24:36.683
